You need JDK 1.6 and SBT (http://code.google.com/p/simple-build-tool/).

* To download dependencies: sbt update
* To compile: sbt compile
* To run: sbt run
* To package to .jar file: sbt package

Copy release/config.properties.sample to release/config.properties and edit
to suit your environment.

Then start SBT then from SBT command prompt, run:
> run server release/config.properties

== Release

Change to release directory, then run:
./release

comy-<VERSION>.tar.bz2 will be created in target directory.
